OL,5,FNext stop was the BBC Weather Centre
OL,6,Fwhere she forecast behind the camera
OL,7,Fbefore stepping in front of the green
OL,8,Fscreen at BBC Spotlight in Plymouth in
OL,9,F2014.
OL,11,FFinally Holly got a chance to join ITV
OL,12,FMeridian - the very programme she'd
OL,13,Fgrown up watching - and now she's the
OL,14,Fone doing her best to get it right
OL,15,Fevery night!
OL,17,FPhilippa Drew
