OL,3,CYour Meridian Weather Team
OL,5,FPhilippa decided she wanted to be a
OL,6,FWeather Presenter at the age of 7 so
OL,7,Fit has been a long and interesting
OL,8,Fjourney! After graduating from Reading
OL,9,FUniversity Philippa joined the Met
OL,10,FOffice, initially as a Broadcast
OL,11,FAssistant at the BBC Weather Centre.
