OL,3,CYour Meridian Weather Team
OL,5,FPhilippa qualified as a meteorologist
OL,6,Fin 2003 and then spent 5 years in
OL,7,FLondon forecasting behind the scenes
OL,8,Fat ITV Weather, followed by a further
OL,9,F8 years forecasting for the Royal
OL,10,FArtillery on the Salisbury Plain.
OL,11,FDuring this time, she began presenting
OL,12,Fthe weather for ITV on an ad hoc basis
OL,13,Fbefore officially joining the ITV
OL,14,FWeather team in 2017. When she's not
OL,15,Fcloud-spotting, Philippa particularly
OL,16,Fenjoys running, baking, skiing and
OL,17,Fkeeping tabs on her delinquent rescue
OL,18,Fcat.
